What you need to know:

We will never go anywhere when the well-connected in the club bring in players who cannot string five passes in a row and dump them on the club.We will never go anywhere when those in charge, like the proverbial ostrich, bury their heads deep in the sand. And we will never go anywhere when the attitude reigning supreme at the club is that of  “players and coaches come and go’”as disastrously captured by the late Joab Omino.